---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { getSortedPosts } from '../utils/posts';

const posts = await getSortedPosts();
---

<Layout title="Earl's Place | Home">
    <section class="intro-text">
        <p>Below is a compilation of most but certainly not all of my trip reports. Missing are most fishing trips to area lakes, rivers and I almost never discuss coastal fishing. My fishing locations along the Texas coast are private unless it is a generic location. This is a lesson learned from many years ago when I was a teenager living on a Texas coastal barrier island. If I told you where I fished, good chance it was a lie, will even lie to my dad about where I fish.</p>

        <p>These reports are to provide myself, family and friends memories of good times and also to aid in the recall of details we may have forgotten so they can be referenced for future trips.</p>

        <p>
            <a href="/posts/river-outfitters">River Outfitters</a>
            <a href="https://sites.google.com/site/earlatnipsplace/river-gages">River Gages</a>
            <a href="http://www.ozarkpages.com/cgi-bin/stages.pl?ST=level">Ozark Creek Summary</a>
        </p>

        <p>
            <a href="https://share.garmin.com/EarlAtnip">Where is Earl?</a>
            <a href="/posts/earls-bucket-list">Earl's Bucket List</a>
            <a href="/posts/special-photos">Special Photos</a>
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="post-list">
        <h2>Posts</h2>
		<ul>
			{posts.map((post) => (
				<li class="post-item">
					<a href={`/posts/${post.slug}/`} class="post-title">
						<h3>{post.data.title}</h3>
					</a>
					<p class="post-description">{post.data.description}</p>
				</li>
			))}
		</ul>
	</section>
</Layout>

<style>
    /*
      This styles the introductory text section at the top of your homepage.
    */
    .intro-text {
        margin-bottom: 2rem; /* Adds space below this section */
    }
    .intro-text p {
        margin-bottom: 1rem; /* Adds space below each paragraph in this section */
        line-height: 1.6; /* Sets the spacing between lines of text */
    }
    .intro-text a {
        margin-right: 1rem; /* Adds space to the right of each link */
        text-decoration: none; /* Removes the underline from these links */
        color: #007bff; /* Sets a default blue color for these links */
    }
    .intro-text a:hover {
        text-decoration: underline; /* Adds an underline when you hover over these links */
    }

	/*
	  This styles the main list of blog posts on your homepage.
	*/
	.post-list h2 {
		font-size: 1.5rem; /* Sets the size of the section title (if any) */
		font-weight: 500; /* Sets the boldness of the section title */
		margin-bottom: 2rem; /* Adds space below the section title */
		text-align: center; /* Centers the section title */
		color: #666; /* Sets the color of the section title */
	}
	.post-list ul {
		list-style: none; /* Removes bullet points from the list */
		padding: 0; /* Removes default inner spacing */
		margin: 0; /* Removes default outer spacing */
	}
	.post-item {
		margin-bottom: 2rem; /* Adds space below each post in the list */
		border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light); /* Adds a thin line below each post to separate them */
		padding-bottom: 2rem; /* Adds space between the post content and the separating line */
	}
	.post-item:last-child {
		border-bottom: none; /* Removes the line under the very last post */
		margin-bottom: 0; /* Removes extra space below the very last post */
	}
	.post-title {
		text-decoration: none; /* Removes the underline from the post title links */
	}
	.post-title h3 {
		color: var(--accent-maroon); /* Sets the color of the post title */
		margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0; /* Adds space below the post title */
		font-size: 1.4rem; /* Sets the size of the post title text */
		font-weight: 600; /* Makes the post title text bold */
		transition: color 0.2s ease-in-out; /* Makes the color change smooth when hovering */
	}
	.post-title:hover h3 {
		color: #000; /* Changes the post title color to black when hovering */
	}
	.post-description {
		margin: 0; /* Removes default spacing */
		line-height: 1.6; /* Sets the spacing between lines of text */
		color: #555; /* Sets the color of the post description text */
	}
</style>
